caption.title: Reactivities of the 15 neutralizing antibodies to PRV gB and gB-D_IV determined by ELISA.
caption.p: The abscissa and ordinate represent the OD 450 values of antibodies reacting to plates coated with gB-D_IV and gB ectodomain, respectively. Each antibody is represented by a blue spot and labeled aside correspondingly.
